# Link-checker ignore patterns (lychee, WI-PS-06).
# The planning repo (plan/) is tracked separately and is gitignored here, so links into it
# do not resolve in a CI checkout of the public repo. Exclude them from the docs link check.
plan/
# Placeholder project remote — the public GitHub repo/Discussions may not exist yet.
github\.com/opencanopy
# Rust API docs under docs/api/ (control, sim) are generated by the Pages build (cargo doc)
# and are not committed, so the offline link check can't resolve them (see docs/firmware-api.md).
docs/api/
